'''感染行动'''（{{lang-ru|Операция «Инфекция»|Operatsiya Infektsiya}}，{{lang-en|Operation INFEKTION}}）是[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]情報機構[[克格勃|克格勃]]在20世纪80年代开展的一次虚假宣传行动的俗称，该行动旨在误导民众相信[[艾滋病毒|艾滋病毒]]和[[艾滋病|艾滋病]]是美国[[迪特里克堡|迪特里克堡]]制造的生物武器<ref name="infektion">{{cite journal|url=https://www.cia.gov/library/center-for-the-study-of-intelligence/csi-publications/csi-studies/studies/vol53no4/pdf/U-%20Boghardt-AIDS-Made%20in%20the%20USA-17Dec.pdf|title=Soviet Bloc Intelligence and Its AIDS Disinformation Campaign (Operation INFEKTION)|journal=[[Studies_in_Intelligence|Studies in Intelligence]]|first=Thomas|last=Boghardt|date=2009-12|volume=53|issue=4<!-- https://www.cia.gov/library/center-for-the-study-of-intelligence/csi-publications/csi-studies/studies/vol53no4/soviet-bloc-intelligence-and-its-aids.html -->|access-date=2021-01-21|archive-date=2020-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227170847/https://www.cia.gov/library/center-for-the-study-of-intelligence/csi-publications/csi-studies/studies/vol53no4/pdf/U-|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Lessons From Operation "Denver," the KGB's Massive AIDS Disinformation Campaign|url=https://thereader.mitpress.mit.edu/operation-denver-kgb-aids-disinformation-campaign/|date=2020-05-26|website=The MIT Press Reader|language=en|access-date=2020-05-29|archive-date=2021-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213150658/https://thereader.mitpress.mit.edu/operation-denver-kgb-aids-disinformation-campaign/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
<!--Historian Thomas Boghardt popularized the codename "INFEKTION" based on the claims of former East German Ministry of State Security ([[Stasi|Stasi]]) officer Günther Bohnsack, who claimed that the Stasi codename for the campaign was either "INFEKTION" or perhaps also "VORWÄRTS II" ("FORWARD II").<ref name="infektion" /> However, historians Christopher Nehring and Douglas Selvage found in the former Stasi and Bulgarian State Security archives materials that prove the actual Stasi codename for the AIDS disinformation campaign was '''Operation "DENVER"'''.<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://www.wilsoncenter.org/blog-post/operation-denver-kgb-and-stasi-disinformation-regarding-aids|title=Operation "Denver": KGB and Stasi Disinformation regarding AIDS|date=2019-07-19|website=Wilson Center|language=en|access-date=2019-07-23}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last=Selvage|first=Douglas|date=2019-10-01|title=Operation "Denver": The East German Ministry of State Security and the KGB's AIDS Disinformation Campaign, 1985–1986 (Part 1)|journal=Journal of Cold War Studies|volume=21|issue=4|pages=71–123|doi=10.1162/jcws_a_00907|issn=1520-3972|doi-access=free}}</ref> The operation involved "an extraordinary amount of effort — funding radio programs, courting journalists, distributing would-be scientific studies", according to journalist Joshua Yaffa, and even became the subject of a report by [[Dan_Rather|Dan Rather]] on the “[[CBS_Evening_News|CBS Evening News]]”.<ref name="Yaffa-NYer-7-9-2020">{{cite journal |last1=Yaffa |first1=Joshua |title=Is Russian Meddling as Dangerous as We Think? |journal=The New Yorker |date=7 September 2020 |url=https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2020/09/14/is-russian-meddling-as-dangerous-as-we-think |access-date=21 September 2020}}</ref>--->1992年蘇聯解體後，[[对外情报局|俄罗斯联邦对外情报局]]局长[[叶夫根尼·普里马科夫|叶夫根尼·普里马科夫]]承认，苏联报纸上一系列宣扬艾滋病美国制造论的文章由克格勃策划<ref name=kello/>。

==經過==
1983年起，[[苏联|苏联]]秘密情报机构[[克格勃|克格勃]]协同其[[东欧|东欧]][[卫星国|卫星国]]情报组织如[[史塔西|史塔西]]等发起了[[丹佛行动|丹佛行动]]，編造「艾滋病是由美國製造」的謠言，該謠言宣稱美国在迪特里克堡研制出[[艾滋病毒|艾滋病毒]]作为生物武器，并在囚犯、[[少数民族|少数民族]]和[[同性恋者|同性恋者]]身上进行了测试，然后称其源于[[非洲|非洲]]<ref name="Nehring01">{{cite web |author=Christopher Nehring |title=新冠病毒、艾滋病、鼠疫和阴谋论 |url=https://www.dw.com/zh/新冠病毒艾滋病鼠疫和阴谋论/a-52718429 |website=德国之声 |date=2020-03-15 |access-date=2022-06-27 |archive-date=2021-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122045306/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E8%89%BE%E6%BB%8B%E7%97%85%E9%BC%A0%E7%96%AB%E5%92%8C%E9%98%B4%E8%B0%8B%E8%AE%BA/a-52718429 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author1=Mark Kramer |coauthors=Douglas Selvage |title=Lessons From Operation “Denver,” the KGB’s Massive AIDS Disinformation Campaign |url=https://thereader.mitpress.mit.edu/operation-denver-kgb-aids-disinformation-campaign/ |journal=The MIT Press Reader |date=2020-05-29 |accessdate=2021-01-20 |archive-date=2021-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213150658/https://thereader.mitpress.mit.edu/operation-denver-kgb-aids-disinformation-campaign/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=何蕙安 |title=【疫情時代的資訊戰】「新冠病毒源頭」的不實訊息 成各國輿論戰新武器 |url=https://tfc-taiwan.org.tw/articles/5085 |agency=Taiwan FactCheck Center |date=2021-02-24 |accessdate=2021-12-28 |archive-date=2021-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211228194142/https://tfc-taiwan.org.tw/articles/5085 }}</ref>。

在計劃中，史塔西最早找到[[東德|東德]][[科學家|科學家]]西格爾（Jakob Segal）夫婦，提供各種假證據使他們信以為真，然後讓他們成了謠言在科學界的代言人，一些美國人也在也相信了有關論調，例如[[紐約|紐約]]學者Lehrman宣稱，美國曾經將該病毒用於暗殺[[民主剛果|民主剛果]]的首相。在科學界證明艾滋病毒來自[[西非|西非]]的[[猿猴|猿猴]]前，「艾滋病是由美國製造」的謠言已傳遍全球，並且有80多個國家的媒體給予過報導。1989年[[柏林圍牆倒塌|柏林圍牆倒塌]]後，[[東德|東德]]的史塔西解密檔案證實了蘇聯克格勃參與編造「艾滋病是由美國製造」的謠言，並有計劃地將此謠言散佈到全球，以打擊美國的信譽，助长[[反美主义|反美主义]]，在国外孤立美国，并在美国和有美国驻军基地的国家之间制造紧张关系（因为经常有说法认为这些基地导致了当地艾滋病爆发）。在計劃中，史塔西最早找到德裔蘇聯生物學家[[科學家|科學家]]雅各布‧西格爾（Jakob Segal）夫婦，向他們提供各種假證據，使他們信以為真並為這種陰謀論撰寫了偽科學依據，使他們成為了該謠言在科學界的代言人。<ref>{{cite news |author1=大象公会 |title=民族传统医学大战艾滋病 |url=https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_6658269 |agency=澎湃新闻·澎湃号·湃客 |date=2020-03-24 |accessdate=2021-07-28 |archive-date=2021-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210724080428/https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_6658269 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="statereport">{{cite report|url=https://www.globalsecurity.org/intell/library/reports/1987/soviet-influence-activities-1987.pdf|publisher=[[U.S._Department_of_State|U.S. Department of State]]|title=Soviet Influence Activities: A Report on Active Measures and Propaganda, 1986-87|date=August 1987|access-date=2021-01-21|archive-date=2021-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210219155758/https://www.globalsecurity.org/intell/library/reports/1987/soviet-influence-activities-1987.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

儘管生物學家和醫學專業人士將西格爾的論斷視作[[謬論|謬論]]，但該陰謀論仍以各種形式廣泛出現。1990年代蘇聯解體後，[[非洲|非洲]]爆發了嚴重的[[埃博拉|埃博拉]]疫情，當時一些認為愛滋病毒由美國在實驗室研製的陰謀論者，再次指責疫情是因[[美軍|美軍]]或[[英軍|英軍]]的研究設施進行生物武器試驗而起<ref name="Nehring01"/>。

1992年，[[对外情报局|俄罗斯联邦对外情报局]]局长[[叶夫根尼·普里马科夫|叶夫根尼·普里马科夫]]承认，苏联报纸上一系列宣扬艾滋病美国制造论的文章由克格勃策划<ref name=kello/>。

[[美国国务院|美国国务院]]的分析师还称，該行动的另一个目的是为苏联自己的{{tsl|en|Soviet_biological_weapons_program|苏联生物武器计划|生物武器计划}}转移视线<ref name="infektion"/>。

